{% comment %}
  VibeMag Product FAQ Accordion
{% endcomment %}

<div class="vm-faq-section">
  <h3 class="vm-faq-title">Întrebări Frecvente</h3>
  
  <div class="vm-faq-container">
    <details class="vm-faq-item">
      <summary class="vm-faq-question">
        <span>Din ce țară provine produsul?</span>
        <span class="vm-faq-icon">
          <svg class="vm-icon-plus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
          <svg class="vm-icon-minus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="vm-faq-answer">
        <p>Produsul este fabricat în Spania de InnovaGoods, unul dintre cei mai mari furnizori europeni de produse inovatoare.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="vm-faq-item">
      <summary class="vm-faq-question">
        <span>Cât durează livrarea?</span>
        <span class="vm-faq-icon">
          <svg class="vm-icon-plus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
          <svg class="vm-icon-minus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="vm-faq-answer">
        <p>Livrăm în 2-5 zile lucrătoare pe teritoriul României. Vei primi un email cu numărul de urmărire după expediere.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="vm-faq-item">
      <summary class="vm-faq-question">
        <span>Pot returna produsul dacă nu sunt mulțumit?</span>
        <span class="vm-faq-icon">
          <svg class="vm-icon-plus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
          <svg class="vm-icon-minus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="vm-faq-answer">
        <p>Da, acceptăm retururi în 14 zile de la primirea coletului, fără nicio întrebare. Contactează-ne pe email sau chat.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="vm-faq-item">
      <summary class="vm-faq-question">
        <span>Produsul vine cu garanție?</span>
        <span class="vm-faq-icon">
          <svg class="vm-icon-plus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
          <svg class="vm-icon-minus" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="vm-faq-answer">
        <p>Toate produsele InnovaGoods sunt însoțite de certificat de calitate european și beneficiază de garanție conform legislației române.</p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
